<surface xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:mith="http://mith.umd.edu/sc/ns1#" ulx="0"
  uly="0" lrx="5406" lry="7276" xml:id="ox-ms_shelley_e1-0024" partOf="#ox-ms_shelley_e1">
  <graphic url="http://shelleygodwinarchive.org/images/ox/ox-ms_shelley_e1-0024.jp2"/>
  <zone type="main">
    <milestone unit="tei:l" spanTo="#e1-0024.01"/>
    <line>Threatenedst to muffle round with black destruction,</line>
    <line rend="right">sending</line>
    <anchor xml:id="e1-0024.01"/>
    <line rend="indent1">A solid cloud to rain hot thunderstones,</line>
    <line rend="indent1">And splinter &amp; knead down my childrens bones,</line>
    <line>All I bring forth, to one void mass battering &amp; blending</line>
    <line rend="indent1">Until each craglike tower &amp; storied column</line>
    <line rend="indent1">Palace, &amp; <unclear reason="case">O</unclear>belisk &amp; Temple
      solemn</line>
    <line>My imperial mountains crowned with <mod>
        <del rend="strikethrough">ligh</del>
        <add place="sublinear">cloud &amp; snow &amp; fire,</add>
      </mod></line>
    <line rend="indent1">My sea-like forests, every blade &amp; blossom</line>
    <line rend="indent1">Which finds a grave or cradle on my bosom</line>
    <milestone unit="tei:l" spanTo="#e1-0024.02"/>
    <line>Were stamped <unclear reason="illegible">b</unclear>y <mod>
        <del rend="overwritten">m</del>
        <add place="intralinear">th</add>
      </mod>y strong hate into a lifeless</line>
    <line rend="right"><add><metamark function="separate">&#8970;</metamark></add>mire<anchor
        xml:id="e1-0024.02"/></line>
    <milestone unit="tei:l" spanTo="#e1-0024.03"/>
    <line rend="indent1">How art thou sunk, withdrawn, coverd&#x2014;</line>
    <line rend="right">drunk up</line>
    <anchor xml:id="e1-0024.03"/>
    <line rend="indent1">By thirsty nothing, as the brackish cup</line>
    <line>Drained by a Desart-troop&#x2014;a little drop for all!</line>
    <line rend="indent1">And from beneath, around, within, above,</line>
    <line rend="indent1">Filling thy void annihilation, Love</line>
    <milestone unit="tei:l" spanTo="#e1-0024.04"/>
    <line>Bursts in like light on caves cloven by</line>
    <line rend="right">the thunderball</line>
    <anchor xml:id="e1-0024.04"/>
    <milestone unit="tei:speaker" spanTo="#e1-0024.05"/>
    <line rend="indent3">The <mod>
        <del rend="overwritten">m</del>
        <add place="intralinear">M</add>
      </mod>oon</line>
    <anchor xml:id="e1-0034.05"/>
    <line rend="indent1">The Snow upon my lifeless mountains</line>
    <line rend="indent1">Is loosened into living fountains</line>
    <line>My solid Oceans flow &amp; sing &amp; shine</line>
  </zone>
</surface>
